_sText:
de_islanders is a port of the de_island map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

- Complete the task: A bomb defusal map, installed in the on the indicated terrain.

- The minimap is attached.

Description from the author of the map:

- The map has a simple and easy to learn layout, it features 2 bombsites and it was tested before the final release with real players on CSGO2.ASTRAMANIA.RO for a few weeks since the first beta was released. 

- The map it's optimized as much as possible.

 - Being made for competitive play it doesn't have to many details to impede the gameplay. 

- Enjoy!
